<h1>狭</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">xiá</span><span class=alesi>(xia2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 狭 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 狭</h2><div class=abo>
