racter-list/hsk/level-6" title="List of HSK 6 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 6 charaters &raquo;</a></small></p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 2018</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 1600</p><p><b>Traditional variant:</b> <a href="/character/狹">狹</a></p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/促狭" title="cu4 xia2">促狭</a>, <a href="/dictionary/偏狭" title="pian1 xia2">偏狭</a>, <a href="/dictionary/束狭" title="shu4 xia2">束狭</a>, <a href="/dictionary/狭小" title="xia2 xiao3">狭小</a>, <a href="/dictionary/狭径" title="xia2 jing4">狭径</a>, <a href="/dictionary/狭窄" title="xia2 zhai3">狭窄</a>, <a href="/dictionary/狭义" title="xia2 yi4">狭义</a>, <a href="/dictionary/狭谷" title="xia2 gu3">狭谷</a>, <a href="/dictionary/狭路" title="xia2 lu4">狭路</a>, <a href="/dictionary/狭长" title="xia2 chang2">狭长</a>, <a href="/dictionary/狭隘" title="xia2 ai4">狭隘</a>, <a href="/dictionary/窄狭" title="zhai3 xia2">窄狭</a>, <a href="/dictionary/褊狭" title="bian3 xia2">褊狭</a>, <a href="/dictionary/促狭鬼" title="cu4 xia2 gui3">促狭鬼</a>, <a href="/dictionary/心胸狭窄" title="xin1 xiong1 xia2 zhai3">心胸狭窄</a>, <a href="/dictionary/心胸狭隘" title="xin1 xiong1 xia2 ai4">心胸狭隘</a>, <a href="/dictionary/狭路相逢" title="xia2 lu4 xiang1 feng2">狭路相逢</a>, <a href="/dictionary/二尖瓣狭窄" title="er4 jian1 ban4 xia2 zhai3">二尖瓣狭窄</a>, <a href="/dictionary/狭义相对论" title="xia2 yi4 xiang1 dui4 lun4">狭义相对论</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">狹|狭[<span style="color:#cc7700;">xiá</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- narrow<br>- narrow-minded<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">陿|狭[<span style="color:#cc7700;">xiá</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- old varia